title: RaspberryPi_Bitcoin_Miner_HowTo.pdf
description:
DIY Complete parts list for your own Bitcoin mining rig with Raspberry Pi micro-computer. 

Mining cryptocurency need energy, jump in the bitcoin game with this low power rig.

Tired of your noisy and burning GPU rig ? Sell it all and go for some Raspberry pi and dual usb miner.


Simple as 1-2-3

Order parts, do DIY assembly, install softwares and mining you are !

Everything is there for you to succeed.

How-To and softwares are a click away from this document.

Good luck for you all !
